Siguro if there's one thing I'd like to reflect on on the past month, it will be about how much differences there are between this January and last year's. 

It made me reminisce about how we treated each other within our first month of meeting each other. 

Ang cute cute lang lagi bby pag naalala ko nung pa demure and pabebe pa tayo pareho HAHAHAHAHAH. Cute cute rugo naten nagdadate sa CDC. Ngayon pareho na naten hobby rot in bed HAHAHAHA. I love you bby!!! So much has changed since last year and I've grown so much more comfortable with you. You've become an integral part of my everyday life and I can no longer remember what life was like before I met you. You've made my life a thousand times better!!!  

Happy Monthsary!
